data.text:
Jean Leres Dieudonne, born to a large family of 11 siblings, has passed on November 8, 2017, leaving behind his wife, Elvire Dieudonne, and numbers of children and grandchildren. The funeral services took place on November 18, 2017 at Hope Church of the Nazarene, Miami FL, by Rev. Abner Noel. He will forever be remembered in the family.
